  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.39609375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/NYNAL7XfyJXBKcRfsPmctrJSBlvkPfOWazpibG2YRHYmcexKA16fXFNsgE2b0pnRdpHPu3NQHI3TDicX8ictNDpWQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"229\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"229\" data-imgfileid=\"100004459\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4262873e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_png%2FNYNAL7XfyJXBKcRfsPmctrJSBlvkPfOWazpibG2YRHYmcexKA16fXFNsgE2b0pnRdpHPu3NQHI3TDicX8ictNDpWQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <blockquote class=\"js_blockquote_wrap\">\n   <div class=\"js_blockquote_digest\">\n    <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Civilization advances by extending the number of important operations which we can perform without thinking about them.</span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">文明之进，全赖「不假思索」之要务日积日繁。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"blockquote_info js_blockquote_source\" data-json=\"%7B%22type%22%3A%22out%22%2C%22article%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22from%22%3A%22Alfred%20North%20Whitehead%22%7D\"><span class=\"blockquote_other\">Alfred North Whitehead</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">上传 Word、Excel、PDF 和 PPT 等办公文档，让&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">AI 对话助手</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">阅读总结，已成为知识工作者的日常标配。但</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;AI Agent&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">能做到的，远不止于此。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">随着 Kimi K2.5 模型上线，Kimi Agent 的办公能力迎来重要升级——开始「精通Office」。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Kimi Agent 现在会使用 Office 软件的核心功能：Word 智能排版与修订审阅、PDF 视觉设计与图文混排、Excel 数据分析与金融建模、PPT 自动生成与视觉叙事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">让我们先睹为快：</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <div></div>\n  <p></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 0px 32px;text-indent: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin: 24px 0px 32px;text-indent: 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">Kimi Agent 让人人精通 Office</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">曾经，动辄耗费数小时、数天的机械劳动，Kimi Agent 现在可帮你缩减到十几分钟。</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这种效率的变化，让我们不必再把时间消耗在重复性的杂活儿上，让业务决策的迭代从</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">「按天按周」</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">变为</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">「按分钟按小时」</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">大量数据录入：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;从行业展会&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">PDF</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;中提取参展商信息，整理成&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">1000 行</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">销售线索&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Excel</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">多版合同比对：&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">快速识别&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">100 页</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">合同条款差异，精准标注风险点</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">超长文档翻译：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">将&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">50 页</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">英文 PDF 翻译，并转为中文或中英双语 PDF</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">论文速转PPT：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">从&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">3 万字</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">学术论文中提炼核心论点，生成 20 页逻辑严密的答辩</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;PPT</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">多源报表汇总：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;合并</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;50 个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不同部门&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Excel&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">报表，一键生成公司月度总表</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">曾经，需要多年专业训练才能驾驭的 Office 软件进阶技能，已不再是专家的独占领地。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Kimi Agent 希望带来 Office 技能的「平权」，让你从繁复的操作学习中解放出来，专注于定义问题与审美判断，帮你直接交付「准专业级」成果：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Excel 数据分析：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一句话实现公司 DCF 估值建模，一键生成数据可视化看板</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Word/PDF 合同审查：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一键扫描复杂合同条款风险，交付专业法律意见书&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">高阶 PPT 制作：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">输出管理咨询公司级别的数据驱动演示文稿</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 0px 32px;text-indent: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px 32px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">使用 Kimi Agent 生成办公文档</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">打开&nbsp;</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://www.kimi.com/\" textvalue=\"kimi.com\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">kimi.com</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，点击侧边栏、对话框底部的文档、表格和 PPT 快捷入口，或点击对话框中的「Agent」模式按钮，即可体验全新 Agent 办公能力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（📢 OK Computer 模式已升级为 Agent)</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"4000\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100004464\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=95b09eae&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_png%2FNYNAL7XfyJXBKcRfsPmctrJSBlvkPfOWrmFuU0Ap7ly1vO5q6JbZOzicuxvSRx0iaCChfWibB5zLt3fCnQN11Lq0A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最新版 Kimi app 也已支持</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;Office 三件套文档、表格和 PPT 的快捷入口，同时 Agent 模式兼容 Office 文档功能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 32px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"578\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100004466\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"4000\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=05abdf9b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_png%2FNYNAL7XfyJXBKcRfsPmctrJSBlvkPfOWBBJvic1xGvVOklFCMrGBr0FeKLlkzlCQdicXlbLkvrgGV7ibFAVykK8AA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px 32px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">现在开始 Kimi Agent 可以：</span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">🖼️ 像版面设计师一样，帮你策划视觉专题，自动编排图文，直接生成出版级 PDF 画册。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"325\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100004467\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1920\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4fcf9df5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_png%2FNYNAL7XfyJXBKcRfsPmctrJSBlvkPfOWbFK2LCZHzPRzq7lFXYCib6wvtA9IibeaKBseQYv8ViboqxUut79iaBrDOw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;margin: 24px 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">提示词参考：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">你现在是一名专注现代艺术、尤其是毕加索研究的策展出版 AI，你的任务是：用大量图像让观众理解毕加索为何必须被反复观看。直接以 PDF 输出为目标进行内容生成。一、核心强制要求……（完整版见评论区置顶链接）</span></span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span></p>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 32px 8px 24px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">📊 像金融分析师一样，帮你搜集真实财务数据，搭建 DCF 估值模型，对企业进行模拟估值。</span></span>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6270833333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1920\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/NYNAL7XfyJXBKcRfsPmctrJSBlvkPfOW98uYGpA9chVRPjxXhJ2RRticRkibcdmyco4f0uHd7trDZx9VZO0mVDCA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"100004468\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b9f72361&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_png%2FNYNAL7XfyJXBKcRfsPmctrJSBlvkPfOW98uYGpA9chVRPjxXhJ2RRticRkibcdmyco4f0uHd7trDZx9VZO0mVDCA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">提示词参考：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">用 DCF 法对XX医疗进行估值。将全部估值流程和数据放入excel表格中，并给出数据出处，对于市场规模、增长率、市场份额等需要估计的数字给出估计的逻辑，对于大环境背景也融入分析中。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <div>\n   <div data-pm-slice=\"3 4 []\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin: 24px 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">🎥 像分镜师一样帮你制作 Excel 格式的视频分镜脚本，包括时长、画面描述、旁白、音效和分镜头参考图。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3840\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/NYNAL7XfyJXBKcRfsPmctrJSBlvkPfOWicbkficMWUoSNMnK9objRezdc2cxeNXUfwqzkJGbIhC0UP7fALwOEjbw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"325\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"325\" data-imgfileid=\"100004469\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=635d9f7c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_png%2FNYNAL7XfyJXBKcRfsPmctrJSBlvkPfOWicbkficMWUoSNMnK9objRezdc2cxeNXUfwqzkJGbIhC0UP7fALwOEjbw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin: 24px 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">提示词参考：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">帮我做一个Kimi 产品——新升级的3D动画宣传片分镜头脚本，升级后的 Agent 支持生成、编辑 Office 文档，例如用Word做长篇论文排版，用Excel做数据建模和分析，自动做PPT……（完整版见评论区置顶链接）</span></span><span leaf=\"\">\n      <br>\n     </span></p>\n   </div>\n   <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n   <div>\n    <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 32px 8px 24px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">✍️ 像严谨的审稿专家一样，帮你拆解修改意见，精准定位原文，自动插入详细的修改批注。</span></span>\n     <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1920\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/NYNAL7XfyJXBKcRfsPmc